BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Visit Palmer": "https://visitpalmer.com/event/palmer-mountain-brew-hand-embroidery-class/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:visit_palmer
X-SOURCE:Visit Palmer
DTSTART;TZID=America/Anchorage:20260321T150000
DTEND;TZID=America/Anchorage:20260321T190000
DTSTAMP:20260321T180104
CREATED:20260221T162040Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260221T162040Z
UID:7996-1774105200-1774119600@visitpalmer.com
SUMMARY:Palmer : Mountain Brew Hand Embroidery Class
DESCRIPTION:The Mountain Brew design by Landly AK is the perfect introduction to hand embroidery. In this class you will learn 6 stitches in a 4-hour period. All supplies needed will be provided but feel to bring any of your own things if you prefer. I recommend you bring glasses that you wear\, even occasionally.You will go home with your piece\, 5-inch hoop\, size 5 needle and thread needed to complete any leftover work at home. This class is for 21 and older\, a drink will be included.Please keep in mind that embroidery is a slower craft and that it is likely you do not finish the piece before class is over.If you are unable to register online and would like to attend\, please message me so I can plan for your attendance. No refunds but if you are unable to attend class after signing up\, we can move you to a later class within the year of 2026\, as long as you reach out to me any time before class starts. \nBleeding Heart Brewery 562 S. Denali St. Palmer AK
URL:https://visitpalmer.com/event/palmer-mountain-brew-hand-embroidery-class/
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Connect Mat-Su": "https://www.connectmatsu.org/event/24th-annual-spaghetti-dinner-auction/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:connect_matsu
X-SOURCE:Connect Mat-Su
DTSTART;TZID=America/Anchorage:20260321T160000
DTEND;TZID=America/Anchorage:20260321T210000
DTSTAMP:20260321T180057
CREATED:20260210T001027Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260322T012212Z
UID:10012838-1774108800-1774126800@www.connectmatsu.org
SUMMARY:24th Annual Spaghetti Dinner & Auction
DESCRIPTION:🌟 Join us for a night filled with pasta\, fun\, laughter\, and community love! 🌟\nWe’re excited to welcome you to the 24th Annual Spaghetti Dinner & Auction benefiting Special Olympics Alaska Mat-Su Community Program!\n📅 Saturday\, March 21st\n📍 Mat-Su Career & Tech High School\n⏰ Doors open at 4:30 PM\n🍽️ Dinner served 5:00–7:00 PM\n🎉 Our one-of-a-kind $1 Auction runs 6:30–9:00 PM — don’t forget your $1 bills!\n📝 Silent & Dessert Auctions will run throughout the evening as well.\n🎟️ $15 General Admission\nIncludes a full spaghetti dinner (spaghetti\, salad\, green beans\, garlic bread\, cookie\, and beverage) and admission to all auctions.\nTickets available online or at the door — but dinner is not guaranteed for at-the-door purchases\, so grab yours early at myalaskatix.com or call 907-631-8591.\n💙 This event supports 250+ incredible Special Olympics Alaska Mat-Su athletes! It is only through the generosity of our community that we are able to continue providing year-round sports training and competitions.\nIf you would like to sponsor or donate\, please contact 907-631-8591 or message us!\nCome celebrate our athletes\, enjoy a delicious meal\, and help us continue building a stronger\, more inclusive Mat-Su!
URL:https://www.connectmatsu.org/event/24th-annual-spaghetti-dinner-auction/
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.connectmatsu.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/spaghetti-dinner-and-auction-fundraiser-3.21.26.jpg
END:VEVENT
