X-SOURCE-ID:connect_matsu
X-SOURCE:Connect Mat-Su
DTSTART;TZID=America/Anchorage:20260324T120000
DTEND;TZID=America/Anchorage:20260324T133000
DTSTAMP:20260321T180057
CREATED:20260223T185256Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260322T012213Z
UID:10012842-1774353600-1774359000@www.connectmatsu.org
SUMMARY:Public Transit Workshops - Virtual
DESCRIPTION:Matsu Valley Planning for Transportation wants to hear\nfrom you! Join us for an upcoming public transit workshop—\navailable both in person and virtually to make it easy for\neveryone to participate. We’ll share results from recent transit\nsurveys in the Mat-Su Borough\, hear from local transit providers\,\nand open the floor for conversation and ideas.
URL:https://www.connectmatsu.org/event/public-transit-workshops-virtual/
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=application/pdf:https://www.connectmatsu.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/MVP-Transit-Workshop-Flyer-1.pdf-1.pdf
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Connect Mat-Su": "https://www.connectmatsu.org/event/the-roaming-playroom-together-time-at-lekker-coffee-8/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:connect_matsu
X-SOURCE:Connect Mat-Su
DTSTART;TZID=America/Anchorage:20260324T123000
DTEND;TZID=America/Anchorage:20260324T143000
DTSTAMP:20260321T180057
CREATED:20260309T193801Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260322T012212Z
UID:10012862-1774355400-1774362600@www.connectmatsu.org
SUMMARY:The Roaming Playroom: "Together Time" at Lekker Coffee
DESCRIPTION:That Thing Goin On is excited to announce a new community offering: The Roaming Playroom!\nThe Roaming Playroom will be hosting weekly “Together Time” at Lekker Coffee and Baking Co right in downtown Palmer.\n“Together Time” means sharing life in shared spaces – where grownups stay\, kids play\, and community grows.\nThe Roaming Playroom curates pop-up play spaces for parents to slow down\, eat\, and drink in public without rushing\, while also spending quality time with their children and connecting with other community members.\nStarting March 10\, come visit us at Lekker Coffee and Baking Co on:\nTuesdays from 12:30pm-2:30pm\nand\nSaturdays from 2:30pm-4:30pm\nYou bring your people\, I’ll bring my people\, and lets build some community together!
URL:https://www.connectmatsu.org/event/the-roaming-playroom-together-time-at-lekker-coffee-8/
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/webp:https://www.connectmatsu.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/The-roaming-playroom.webp
END:VEVENT
