UID:10012794-1774432800-1774450800@www.connectmatsu.org
SUMMARY:2026 Mat-Su Employer Expo
DESCRIPTION:This annual Job Fair brings together more than 100 employers and partners\n• Connect with employers hiring for entry level\, technical\, professional and seasonal positions\n• Speak with university\, vocational/technical schools\, apprenticeship and union representatives\n• Dress for success\, be prepared to network with employers\n• Visit the Mat-Su Job Center before the event to prepare your resume and to print free extra copies to bring to the job fair
URL:https://www.connectmatsu.org/event/2026-mat-su-employer-expo/
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=application/pdf:https://www.connectmatsu.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/2026-03-25_MatSu_Employer_Expo_JOBSEEKER.pdf
END:VEVENT
