 to other members and see if 2 or 3 people can come.He will wear his full c
 ostume and bring props. We talked about him focusing on the USA 250th birt
 hday and Alaska during that time.He was wanting to know if it was OK for h
 im to bring a musket as a prop/display. The guns are unloaded and never us
 ed. They just carry them because they are dressed as soldiers. He will nee
 d a white board and table to display various props. Greg's # is 907-602-10
 54I am happy to come that day to greet him and help with any setup or take
  down.Breanna
