X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Visit Palmer": "https://visitpalmer.com/event/mat-su-sentinel-icebreaker-a-benefit-party-at-the-rink/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:visit_palmer
X-SOURCE:Visit Palmer
DTSTART;TZID=America/Anchorage:20260328T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Anchorage:20260328T220000
DTSTAMP:20260321T180104
CREATED:20260221T163312Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260221T163312Z
UID:8004-1774724400-1774735200@visitpalmer.com
SUMMARY:Mat-Su Sentinel Icebreaker: A Benefit Party at the Rink!
DESCRIPTION:Get ready for some fun and join us for a truly one-of-a-kind\, family-friendly community night at the MTA Events Center in Palmer!\nThis isn’t your average concert — it’s a live band + open ice skating and dance floor experience featuring Mat-Su favorites The Super Saturated Sugar Strings. Skate to live music\, dance it out on an ice-free floor\, eat\, drink\, and celebrate local community — all while supporting nonprofit local journalism.\n Your ticket includes:• Live concert entry• Open ice time (skate while the band plays!)• Ice skate rentals (while supplies last)• Big Dipper Homemade Ice Cream (while supplies last)• Soft drinks courtesy of the Odom Corporation (while supplies last)\n Available for purchase at the event:• Beer by Palmer Brewing Company• Food from El Señor Moose food truck• A high-stakes raffle with great prizes\n Not into skating? No problem.Ice skating is totally optional. We’ll have a separate\, ice-free dance floor near the band so you can dance\, listen\, and hang out without ever stepping on the ice.\n Why we’re doing this:This is a benefit event supporting Mat-Su Sentinel\, your local nonprofit newsroom. Come skate\, dance\, eat\, drink — and help keep community news strong in the Mat-Su.\nGrab your friends\, bring the kids\, and help us thaw out winter with a night of music\, movement\, and community.\n\nMTA Events Center\n1317 S Kerry Weiland Ct\, Palmer\, AK
URL:https://visitpalmer.com/event/mat-su-sentinel-icebreaker-a-benefit-party-at-the-rink/
END:VEVENT
