LAST-MODIFIED:20260322T012213Z
UID:10012892-1776765600-1776880800@www.connectmatsu.org
SUMMARY:IDEA Homeschool Curriculum\, Fair (Wasilla)
DESCRIPTION:Join us for our 28th annual springtime event\, the IDEA Homeschool Curriculum Fair: Chart Your Course!\nThe IDEA Curriculum Fair is the premier homeschool event in Alaska where participants have the opportunity to learn about homeschool products from dozens of homeschool curriculum providers and a wide variety of educational workshops.\nWhether enrolled with IDEA or another program\, considering homeschool\, or your kids attend building-based school\, EVERYONE is welcome to attend our public event!\nParticipant registration will open up on April 1st!\nWHERE: Menard Sports Center\nWHEN: Tuesday\, April 21\, 2026 & Wednesday\, April 22\, 2026\nEVENT SCHEDULE:\nTuesday\, April 21\, 2026\n10:00 a.m. – 6:00 p.m. Exhibit Hall open\n10:30 a.m. – 5:00 p.m. Workshops\n1:00 – 2:30 p.m. – Homeschool Tips with Brown Bag Social\nWednesday\, April 22\, 2026\n10:00 a.m. – 3:00 p.m. Exhibit Hall open\n10:30 a.m. – 2:00 p.m. Workshops \nMORE INFO:\nVisit https://fair.ideahomeschool.org/anchorage-valley to learn more!
URL:https://www.connectmatsu.org/event/idea-homeschool-curriculum-fair-wasilla/
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/webp:https://www.connectmatsu.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/idea-fair-4.21-and-4.22.26.webp
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Connect Mat-Su": "https://www.connectmatsu.org/event/the-roaming-playroom-together-time-at-lekker-coffee-4/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:connect_matsu
X-SOURCE:Connect Mat-Su
DTSTART;TZID=America/Anchorage:20260421T123000
DTEND;TZID=America/Anchorage:20260421T143000
DTSTAMP:20260321T180057
CREATED:20260309T193759Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260322T012212Z
UID:10012858-1776774600-1776781800@www.connectmatsu.org
SUMMARY:The Roaming Playroom: "Together Time" at Lekker Coffee
DESCRIPTION:That Thing Goin On is excited to announce a new community offering: The Roaming Playroom!\nThe Roaming Playroom will be hosting weekly “Together Time” at Lekker Coffee and Baking Co right in downtown Palmer.\n“Together Time” means sharing life in shared spaces – where grownups stay\, kids play\, and community grows.\nThe Roaming Playroom curates pop-up play spaces for parents to slow down\, eat\, and drink in public without rushing\, while also spending quality time with their children and connecting with other community members.\nStarting March 10\, come visit us at Lekker Coffee and Baking Co on:\nTuesdays from 12:30pm-2:30pm\nand\nSaturdays from 2:30pm-4:30pm\nYou bring your people\, I’ll bring my people\, and lets build some community together!
URL:https://www.connectmatsu.org/event/the-roaming-playroom-together-time-at-lekker-coffee-4/
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/webp:https://www.connectmatsu.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/The-roaming-playroom.webp
END:VEVENT
