CREATED:20260221T165702Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260221T165702Z
UID:8018-1777050000-1777057200@visitpalmer.com
SUMMARY:2026 Kickoff Kitchen: Moving Mountains Together
DESCRIPTION:Join United Way of Mat-Su for our annual celebration of community\, giving and volunteerism.Presentation of our Dorothy A. Jones Lifetime Achievement\, Volunteer of the Year\, Community Champion and Business Partner of the Year awards will take place during the event program.Bring your sweet tooth and bid on AMAZING handmade desserts at our Dessert Auction! Live auction to follow formal program.Enjoy hearty passed appetizers catered by the Mat-Su Career Tech Culinary Team and local brews from Bleeding Heart Brewery.$70 individual or $400 for a table of 6.Questions? Please call (907)745-5822 or email give@ unitedwaymatsu.org.**Desserts and live auction items/packages are still needed!** \nThe Government Peak Chalet\, 10690 N. Mountain Trails Dr. Palmer \n 
URL:https://visitpalmer.com/event/2026-kickoff-kitchen-moving-mountains-together/
END:VEVENT
