SUMMARY:Bonsai Basics
DESCRIPTION:Learn how to bonsai! This class is hands on and you will go home with a beautiful bonsai tree that you created! Everything to make your tree is included. Pot\, soil\, plant\, tools and expert instructions. Hope you can join us for a fun and informative event. Saturday April 25 at 1:00 p.m. EweTopia Farms 3879 S Caudill in Palmer/Butte 907 746 4134Cost is 85..00
